\begin_layout Example

\series bold
(Q11)
\series default
: Assume that 
\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

 is differentiable of 
\begin_inset Formula $\left[a,b\right]$
\end_inset

 and satisfies 
\begin_inset Formula $g'\left(a\right)<0<g'\left(b\right)$
\end_inset

.
