\begin_layout Enumerate
Show that there exists a point 
\begin_inset Formula $x\in\left(a,b\right)$
\end_inset

 where 
\begin_inset Formula $g\left(a\right)>g\left(x\right)$
\end_inset

, and a point 
\begin_inset Formula $y\in\left(a,b\right)$
\end_inset

